{"tid":337758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可口可樂宣布下月美國推新款無糖可樂　取代Coke Zero","createTime":"2017-07-27T14:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T02:52:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73b12c93bf5d43ed35fc7a18db6cc664951d898f","tid":337758,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170727/s00005/29b055a8e066d3a3bc78214ff9be1caa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F29b055a8e066d3a3bc78214ff9be1caa.jpg&h=9d1f029b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可口可樂宣布，將不再生產Zero可樂（Coke Zero），下月先在美國推出一款全新的無糖可樂全面替代。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂周三（26日）宣布，將不再生產Zero可樂，在8月起會推出新產品「零糖可樂」（Coca-Cola Zero Sugar）。可口可樂行政總裁James Quincey表示，新產品是Zero可樂的「再研發」版本。<br />\n<br />\nCoke Zero和Zero Sugar雖然都是無糖可樂，但味道不一樣，「零糖可樂」會與原味的可口可樂更為相似，而包裝會以黑和紅色為主。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂公司表示，用了超過5年時間進行研究、研發食譜及試驗才推出產品，而命名為Zero Sugar的原因是，希望新產品名稱能盡可能清楚和直白，確保消費者知道產品是無糖飲料。<br />\n<br />\nZero Sugar已在歐洲、中東、非洲等市場取得成功，下月於美國推出。將停產的Coke Zero於2005年推出，去年銷量增長更有3.5％，但Zero Sugar的銷量達雙位數的增長，因此可口可樂公司預計新產品在美國會得到好評。"},{"pid":"5600bf76fcf050e96d41376cacf5627ba08938e3","tid":337758,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170727/s00005/1501161051984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F1501161051984&d=XkISncD%2FKMDCQpxOreQmQzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=88f60922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F1501161051984&h=89fca4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170727/s00005/1501161051984</a>"},{"pid":"95062136034b0ffb128bfb4817e24bda66990ed5","tid":337758,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"